          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Newborn Care Improvement Act</strong></p> <p>This bill increases from 7 to 14 the number of days that the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) may furnish health care services, including post-delivery care, to the newborn child of a woman veteran who delivered the child in a VA facility or another facility pursuant to a VA contract for such services. </p>]]></text>
